Several modifications have been made for RefGrasp, including:
1. modified train.py for training with layer freezing
2. modified trainer.py for loading checkpoints
3. modified task/refcoco.py, data/refgrasp_dataset.py for RefGrasp dataset
4. added polyformer/convnext.py, polyformer/polyformer_rgbd.py, 
   modified polyformer/polyformer.py, polyformer/unify_transformer.py for RGBD model
5. other minor modifications